                                <td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td><a href="viewtopic.php?p=45173#45173"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Wed May 26, 2004 7:29 am<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Todays Patch Message 5-26-04</span></td>
