                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Actually, the problem with MoBs regenning on loss of aggro was detrimental to Monks. If a monk was killing a mob and got it to 25 percent health, then FD'd to regen a bit of health, the MoBs would immediately regen to full. It effectively ruined a monks chance at ANY kind of soloing.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Although I no longer play a monk, I am glad to see this change go into effect.
<br />

<br />

<br />
