<br />

<br />
Before/now: 1) Highlevel aggroes/pulls mob, 2) Highlevel brings it to 5% (or whatever), 3) Highlevel memblurs/zones, 4) Lowlevel finishes kill for full xp.
<br />

<br />
With change: Add step 1a) Lowlevel casts a low-aggro spell at 97% and enters hate list without aggro. 4b) Lowlevel receives 97% of full xp.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
        </tr>
